HYGH: iShares Interest Rate Hedged High Yield Bond ETF

The fund seeks to track the investment results of the underlying index, which is designed to minimize the interest-rate risk of a portfolio composed of U.S. dollar-denominated, high yield corporate bonds, represented in the underlying index by the underlying fund.
